# 🔐 Threat Detection System using MITRE ATT&CK

A full-stack cybersecurity project that simulates and detects common attack patterns such as brute force and traffic spikes, and maps them to MITRE ATT&CK techniques. Built as a SOC-style monitoring dashboard with real-time alerts and log analysis.

---

## 📌 Features

- 🔑 User Authentication (JWT-based login/register)
- 🟢 Monitoring ON/OFF control (SOC simulation)
- 📊 Real-time Dashboard:
  - Active IP tracking
  - Suspicious IP detection
  - Alert generation
  - Attack classification
- 🚨 Attack Detection:
  - Brute Force (multiple failed logins)
  - Traffic Spike / DoS-like behavior (simulated)
- 🧠 MITRE ATT&CK Mapping:
  - Example: T1110 – Brute Force
- 🗂️ Alert history stored in SQLite

