## 🧪 Attack Simulation

⚠️ This project uses **safe, local simulations only**

### Brute Force Simulation
- Multiple failed login attempts
- Account lock after 3 attempts (30 min)
- Detected and mapped to MITRE T1110

### Traffic Spike Simulation
- High number of requests from same IP
- Flagged as suspicious (DoS-like behavior)

